summary: Based version of The Dragonborn Comes and Dovahkiin.
descriptionHtml:
Based version of The Dragonborn Comes and Dovahkiin.
Want to download the MP3? read the description, enjoy and follow me on social networks!

This was our own arrangement of the main theme from Skyrim Elder Scrolls which was composed by Jeremy Soule

Voices: Jeff Winner
Guitars: Cris Anchieta
Bass: Fabio Ribeiro
Drums: Cris Anchieta
Keyboards: Jeff Winner, Fabio Ribeiro, Felipe Fernandes
